         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-B-00002-000-00028-V"/><salute>Lieber,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb55271">hier</rs> verbringe ich, ganz
               unverhofft, einen stillen Tag. Die <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb55271">Stadt</rs> ist verblüffend schön. <date when="1921-03-31">Morgen</date> bin ich
               in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>.</p><closer>Alles Herzliche Ihr <lb/><signed>Felix Salten</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><rs type="place" ref="#pmb55271">Hildesheim</rs>, <date when="1921-03-30">30. 3. 21</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
